      "role": "user",
      "content": "i cant even look at the news anymore. everything feels so heavy. like, why even bother planning a future or trying to build anything when we all know the planet is just spiraling? it feels like we're just watching a slow motion wreck and there's nothing anyone can actually do. it makes everything feel so pointless.",
