      "content": "It is a natural reaction to feel overwhelmed by the sheer scale of things you are currently facing. The idea that everything is already doomed is a heavy burden, but it is not true that there is no escape from the pain of existence. You are not a passenger in a sinking ship; you are the crew with the power to steer the vessel, even if the destination is unknown. The struggle itself is not the destruction; it is the very evidence that you are still alive and still capable of action.",
