      "content": "but that's the thing, the struggle feels so fake when you know the outcome. it feels like we're just being forced to suffer through this long, painful transition for no reason. if you knew a situation was hopeless and just going to end in disaster, wouldn't it be more logical to just... not participate? to just opt out early instead of waiting for the inevitable?",
